                <supplied reason="lost">S</supplied>ilvano <expan><abbr>sac</abbr><ex>rum</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Loco felici <lb n="2"/>Victor ca<lb break="no" n="3"/><expan><abbr>ma</abbr><ex cert="low">ra</ex>rius</expan> ex <lb n="4"/>voto pos<lb break="no" n="5"/>uit
